            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail, peel and chop your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> into small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and grate (or finely chop) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and grate (or finely chop) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Tip: Take the mince off the heat if you need longer to chop to avoid burning!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1615544302644-x200.jpg",
